'''Calcutta Puppet Theatre''' is a [[Bengali language|Bengali]] puppet academy, theatre group, an institute of dance, drama and music. The group was formed in 1973 by [[Suresh Dutta]].<ref name="Contemporary puppets">{{cite web|url=http://www.puppetindia.com/contemp.htm|title=Contemporary puppets|accessdate=11 October 2012}}</ref><ref name="The power of puppetry : Suresh Dutta">{{cite web|url=http://www.harmonyindia.org/hportal/VirtualPageView.jsp?page_id=2303|title=The power of puppetry : Suresh Dutta|accessdate=11 October 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303232319/http://www.harmonyindia.org/hportal/VirtualPageView.jsp?page_id=2303#|archive-date=3 March 2016|dead-url=yes|df=dmy-all}}</ref>
