{{Unreferenced|date=March 2009}}
'''''Svensk Magisk Cirkel''''' (Swedish Magic Circle, SMC) is the national organization for [[Magic (illusion)|magic]] in [[Sweden]]. SMC was founded in 1946, has its seat in [[Stockholm]], and counts around 350 members. The magazine of SMC is called ''Trollkarlen'' ("The Magician"). In 2011 was the 65-year anniversary.
