{{Use mdy dates|date=September 2016}} {{refimprove|date=August 2017}} {{Infobox video game |title=Thrillville: Off the Rails |image=Thrillville2.JPG |developer=[[Frontier Developments]] |publisher=[[LucasArts]] |designer= |engine= |released={{vgrelease|NA|October 9, 2007|AUS|October 17, 2007|EU|October 19, 2007|AUS|October 25, 2007 <small>(Wii)</small>}} |genre=[[Simulation video game|Simulation]] |modes=[[Single-player]], [[Multiplayer video game|multiplayer]] |platforms=[[Nintendo DS]], [[Wii]], [[Xbox 360]], [[PlayStation Portable]], [[PlayStation 2]], [[Microsoft Windows]] }} '''''Thrillville: Off the Rails''''' is a [[theme park]] [[simulation video game]] developed by [[Frontier Developments]] and published by [[LucasArts]]. It is the sequel to the 2006 game ''[[Thrillville]]''. It was released in North America in October 2007.
==Gameplay== Like the original game, ''Thrillville: Off The Rails'' is a strategy and simulation game about being the park manager of all of the Thrillville theme parks. The game allows the placing and deletion of attractions and buildings such as flat rides, food and drink stalls, bathrooms, games, and also contains various minigames to play both in the park and in the game's "Party Play" mode, along with editing and allowing the players to ride their own roller coasters inside each of the Thrillville theme parks.
''Thrillville: Off The Rails'' introduces whoa coaster elements that can be added to coasters while building. They are various tricks and effects that can add to the Thrill level of a coaster.
While the Nintendo DS version of ''Thrillville: Off The Rails'' contains only 7 minigames, the versions for all other consoles contain over 40 minigames. The roller coaster editor is similar to that of the ''[[Roller Coaster Tycoon]]'' series, but all coasters have to start in assigned areas in each of the park's various zones. If the assigned missions are completed in each park, then the player receives thrill points. If enough thrill points are gained, the player can move to the next park manager level.
