The game received "mixed or average reviews" on all platforms according to the [[Review aggregator|review aggregation]] website [[Metacritic]].<ref name=MCDS/><ref name=MCPC/><ref name=MCPS2/><ref name=MCPSP/><ref name=MCWII/><ref name=MCX360/> Most critics cited that the mini-games are a welcome addition, especially for multiplayer; however, the game was criticized for its so-so graphics, including the PC and Xbox 360 versions. Critics also cited some cases of repetitiveness in gameplay.{{citation needed|date=April 2017}}
